data.description: Currently operating as a successful short-term rental.  Sleeps 4-8; Three Queen Beds, One Trendle, One Fold Out Couch. Room for even more growth due to owner stays, lack of management, and only listed on one booking site. Creek on property. Trails on property. Same street as Ash Cave (5-10 min away). Old Mans Cave. Cedar Falls. Deer seen on property often. Financials available upon request. Ideal lot for another cabin or multiple sites for glamping. Neighboring three-acre parcel also negotiable.
